practice, said an earlier police report that 16 people were kiled in
the crash was incorrect.
   The collision occurred Saturday night about 12 miles west of
Harare.
   On May 20, six people were killed and 50 were injured in a
train-bus accident at a crossing 60 miles east of Harare.
