<HEAD>Soviet Foreign Minister Arrives For U.N. Session</HEAD>
<DATELINE>NEW YORK (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Soviet Foreign Minister Eduard Shevardnadze
arrived here Sunday to address a special U.N. session on disarmament
later this week.
   ``We have brought what we believe to be interesting and good
ideas and proposals to this special session and we will set forth
these ideas and suggestions in our statements,'' he told reporters
