<DATELINE>SUBIC NAVAL BASE, Philippines (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   An S-3 Viking anti-submarine
plane from the carrier USS Enterprise crashed Sunday in the South
China Sea, killing at least two crewmen, the U.S. Navy said.
   One of the plane's four crew members was rescued and another was
missing, Navy spokesman Lt. Robert Anderson said Monday. He said the
